<div class="container">

<h1 class="fancy-title">Smart Business Ideas & Algorithmic Systems</h1>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>1. Multilingual BPO & IT Services Hub</h2>
<p>
Optimizes call handling and task distribution among multilingual agents to ensure fast,
fair, and balanced customer service across global clients while reducing agent overload.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Round-Robin Scheduling <br>
SDG 8, SDG 9, SDG 10
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>2. Smart Port Security, Surveillance & Resource Allocation</h2>
<p>
Assigns patrol units and emergency responders to incidents with minimum response time,
ensuring efficient security coverage and rapid crisis handling inside port zones.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Dijkstra + Stable Matching <br>
SDG 9, SDG 11, SDG 16
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>3. Port-Based Ship Repair & Maintenance Hub</h2>
<p>
Schedules multi-stage ship repair tasks across workstations to minimize total completion
time and improve turnaround efficiency at port maintenance facilities.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Assembly Line Scheduling (Dynamic Programming) <br>
SDG 9, SDG 8
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>4. Harbor Logistics Truck Parking & Cargo Processing</h2>
<p>
Controls truck arrival, parking allocation, cargo scanning, and weighing processes to
prevent congestion and ensure smooth cargo flow inside ports.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: FIFO + Greedy + Simulation <br>
SDG 9, SDG 11
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>5. Port Infrastructure, Cold Storage & Industrial Facility Optimization</h2>
<p>
Determines optimal placement of cold storage facilities and delivery routes to minimize
logistics cost, reduce spoilage, and enhance port-based industrial efficiency.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Dynamic Programming + Greedy + TSP <br>
SDG 9, SDG 12, SDG 13
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>6. Beach Wedding & Events Management Hub</h2>
<p>
Manages venue booking, décor, staff allocation, and event schedules without conflicts,
ensuring smooth execution of large-scale coastal events.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Job Scheduling + Resource Allocation <br>
SDG 8, SDG 11
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>7. EV Bike & Water Sports Rental Management</h2>
<p>
Tracks rental availability, charging priorities, and equipment usage to maximize asset
utilization and customer satisfaction at coastal tourism hubs.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Hash Tables + Priority Queues <br>
SDG 7, SDG 9, SDG 13
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>8. Coastal Food Truck Fleet Management</h2>
<p>
Optimizes food-truck routing and inventory distribution across coastal zones to meet demand
while minimizing food waste and logistics cost.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Multiple Knapsack + Bin Packing <br>
SDG 8, SDG 12
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>9. Customer & Public Service Queue Management System</h2>
<p>
Maintains fair queues in banks and government offices while prioritizing emergency cases
to improve citizen experience and service transparency.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Round-Robin + Multi-Level Priority Queues <br>
SDG 10, SDG 16
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>10. Fast Facility Lookup & Navigation System</h2>
<p>
Provides instant prefix-based search for rooms, counters, and offices inside large
facilities such as ports, hospitals, and government buildings.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Trie <br>
SDG 9, SDG 11
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>11. Digital Advertising & Events Scheduling Hub</h2>
<p>
Schedules advertisements and digital events without time overlap while satisfying
multiple constraints such as budget, duration, and audience reach.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Interval Scheduling + Constraint Satisfaction <br>
SDG 9, SDG 8
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>12. Coastal Massage, Spa & Appointment Booking System</h2>
<p>
Handles overlapping spa appointments efficiently, ensuring optimal therapist utilization
and reduced customer waiting time.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Segment Trees + Interval Queries <br>
SDG 3, SDG 8
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>13. Mental Health & Rehabilitation Hub (Shuvansh)</h2>
<p>
Groups patients into compatible therapy clusters to improve treatment effectiveness and
optimize therapist workload.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: K-Means Clustering <br>
SDG 3, SDG 10
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>14. Marine Equipment Manufacturing Unit</h2>
<p>
Schedules machine jobs to maximize production output while minimizing idle time and
operational delays in manufacturing plants.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Greedy Job Sequencing <br>
SDG 9, SDG 8
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>15. GlowFit Club – Gen-Z Fitness Studio</h2>
<p>
Schedules trainers and workout slots dynamically based on real-time demand to maximize
studio utilization and member satisfaction.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Greedy + Priority Queues <br>
SDG 3, SDG 8
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>16. Beauty & Self-Grooming Studio Management</h2>
<p>
Manages multiple beauty services and artist schedules efficiently, avoiding overlaps and
reducing customer wait times.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Interval Scheduling <br>
SDG 8, SDG 10
</div>
</div>

<div class="algo-section">
<h2>17. Sip & Sculpt Café</h2>
<p>
Controls healthy café order flow and ingredient usage smoothly to reduce waste, improve
service speed, and enhance customer experience.
</p>
<div class="sdg">
Algorithm: Greedy + Queue-Based Order Management <br>
SDG 12, SDG 8
</div>
</div>

